---
title: Veggie Patty Melts with Potato Wedges
description: Don't be fooled by this sky-high patty melt. There's actually a scrumptious veggie patty hiding underneath all that gooey cheese! Pickles, BBQ sauce and onions await with every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-patty-melts-a48cbf9c.jpg
